>> Which two formulas below  about attention mechanism are correct? <<

[x] A. [mathjaxinline] w_0 + w_1 + \cdots + w_n = 1 [/mathjaxinline]{{ selected: A. Correct}}
[ ] B. [mathjaxinline] w_0 + w_1 + \cdots + w_n = 0.5 [/mathjaxinline]{{ selected: B. Incorrect, these are the outputs of the softmax function and they sum to one}}
[ ] C. [mathjaxinline] c = \sum\limits_{i=0}^n s_i \cdot h_i [/mathjaxinline]{{ selected: C. Incorrect, the context vector [mathjaxinline] c [/mathjaxinline] is the result of summing all the encoded inputs weighted by their attention weight}}
[x] D. [mathjaxinline] c = \sum\limits_{i=0}^n w_i \cdot h_i [/mathjaxinline]{{ selected: D. Correct}}

